#~ "account provider."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Per fer-ho, necessiteu un compte XMPP. Podeu registrar-vos per obtenir un "
#~ "compte XMPP a [Disroot](https://disroot.org/services/xmpp) o qualsevol "
#~ "altre proveïdor de comptes XMPP."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Then configure your preferred instant messaging client, for example "
#~ "[[Pidgin|http://www.pidgin.im/]], which runs on Windows, GNU/Linux, and "
#~ "macOS, to connect to:"
